short_description: cassell tarring is an architects & architectural services company based in london, united kingdom.
long_description: cassell tarring is a riba chartered practice specialising in the delivery of refined contemporary residential architecture. a dynamic and design led practice with fresh ideas, cassell tarring has gained a reputation for designing and delivering architecturally exciting homes for a range of clients who are looking for a house with a difference. a home that is both beautiful and functional, offering a break from the norm and designed specifically for the client's modern day lifestyles whilst maximising the enjoyment of the living environment. it is this passion for understanding and unlocking the client's dreams and aspirations that has allowed cassell tarring to accomplish an extraordinary amount over the last 10 years since being founded in 2014 (formerly known as michael tarring architects ltd). with a comprehensive knowledge of planning, construction, project management and interior design, their work is characterised by a clean, contemporary and considered approach, which has been recognised by winning prestigious industry awards, such as best architecture single residence southwest and best architecture single residence united kingdom in the uk property awards.
